{"tid":1534220,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"戴V煞面具遊行","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T04:39:18.000Z","uid":114310,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"66d773f8a43416b7f45aa8492283fb4bf602f346","tid":1534220,"uid":114310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d2500510ab0d943eb839081b37c9385af8c464","tid":1534220,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=f61c2d4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"098dd9a9605cf11899f31ed0bbed45b59b3d1873","tid":1534220,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b3cdacd42dfc4870cfb9e9110b686c60b9a05bb","tid":1534220,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:51.000Z","msg":"邊到買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327d1f5575a887ce0fa85ebe208a8f4d680a3f2a","tid":1534220,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:47:01.000Z","msg":"邊到有得買"},{"pid":"f09d397f440dda2e4ffdc93c21ce6babf4e31b23","tid":1534220,"uid":202889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:47:45.000Z","msg":"邊到買"},{"pid":"d06ce8052fa36fc01ef37d50b98506687e9afa7c","tid":1534220,"uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"2014年做過既野，唔好傻，<br />\n本身香港示威者成形左就唔好再搞咁多無謂野"},{"pid":"065149c6e5ea42d01331798f72f571219e5c9b8a","tid":1534220,"uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d06ce8052fa36fc01ef37d50b98506687e9afa7c","tid":1534220,"uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"2014年做過既野，唔好傻，<br />\n本身香港示威者成形左就唔好再搞咁多無謂野"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:48:37.000Z","msg":"*示威者形象"},{"pid":"455c774d12c2769564b416cb9ef6086563f9da33","tid":1534220,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"065149c6e5ea42d01331798f72f571219e5c9b8a","tid":1534220,"uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d06ce8052fa36fc01ef37d50b98506687e9afa7c","tid":1534220,"uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"2014年做過既野，唔好傻，<br />\n本身香港示威者成形左就唔好再搞咁多無謂野"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:48:37.000Z","msg":"*示威者形象"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:25.000Z","msg":"你又講得有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f3d57941465cdcbe0cca8441ad58d0a5f55d26","ti